---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Arbre Bio Africa - Precision Agriculture Pioneer in Côte d'Ivoire"
  description="Meet Sydney Abouna, founder of Arbre Bio Africa. We are transforming agriculture across Africa through precision irrigation, greenhouse solutions, and sustainable farming technologies."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative h-[60vh] flex items-center">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img 
        src="https://imgur.com/4gQ57MK.jpg"
        alt="Arbre Bio Africa - Precision Agriculture Projects" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-55"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-4">About Arbre Bio Africa</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-white max-w-2xl">The story behind Africa's precision agriculture leader — built from the ground up in Côte d'Ivoire</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder Story Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
            <span class="text-primary font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">The Founder</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mt-2 mb-6">Sydney Abouna</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-5 leading-relaxed">
              My name is Sydney Abouna. I founded Arbre Bio Africa, Arbre Bio Côte d'Ivoire and the Organic Tree Group with one clear vision: to make Africa the continent with the most advanced, productive and sustainable agricultural ecosystem in the world.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-5 leading-relaxed">
              I built this company from zero — alone, handling everything from operations and project management to client relations, marketing and partnerships. Every greenhouse we build, every irrigation system we install, every farmer we help is the result of a personal commitment to excellence and innovation.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-5 leading-relaxed">
              I search tirelessly for the world's best agricultural techniques — the most innovative solutions for increasing yield, improving food quality, and making farming profitable and sustainable in Africa's unique climate conditions. I don't believe African farmers should settle for outdated methods when world-class technology exists.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
              Today, Arbre Bio operates in 5 African countries with 500+ completed projects, partnerships with the World Bank, African Development Bank, GIZ, FAO, the Ivorian Ministry of Agriculture, and leading global agritech companies. We are just getting started.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
              <a href="/contact" class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-primary-600 transition-colors duration-300 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                Work With Us
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
              </a>
              <a href="https://wa.me/2250799295643" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-[#25D366] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity duration-300 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                WhatsApp Me Directly
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <img 
              src="https://imgur.com/LD5JZto.jpg" 
              alt="Sydney Abouna - Founder & CEO of Arbre Bio Africa"
              class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover"
              style="max-height: 580px;"
            />
            <div class="mt-4 bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
              <div class="font-bold text-primary text-lg">Sydney Abouna</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Founder & CEO — Arbre Bio Africa · Arbre Bio Côte d'Ivoire · Organic Tree Group</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Do -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">What We Do</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🏗️</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Greenhouse Construction</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">High-tech sawtooth and tunnel greenhouses engineered for African tropical conditions, with full climate control and drip irrigation integration.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">💧</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Precision Irrigation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Smart drip and sprinkler systems that save up to 60% water while dramatically increasing crop yields. Designed and installed for African farms.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🌱</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Growing Solutions</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Premium coco peat substrates and organic growing mediums for hydroponic and soil-based cultivation of high-yield vegetables and fruits.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Vision -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-primary text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🎯</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-white/90 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            To transform African agriculture by providing every farmer with access to the best precision farming technologies in the world — increasing yields, reducing waste, and creating sustainable food systems across the continent.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🌍</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Vision</h3>
          <p class="text-white/90 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            To be the #1 agricultural innovation company in Africa — the most trusted name for modern greenhouse farming, precision irrigation, and smart agriculture solutions from Abidjan to Nairobi.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Our Journey</h2>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0 text-sm">2020</div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 flex-1"><strong>Founded in Abidjan</strong> — Sydney Abouna launches Arbre Bio Africa with a mission to transform agriculture across the continent.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0 text-sm">2021</div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 flex-1"><strong>First Major Project</strong> — First large-scale greenhouse installation completed in Côte d'Ivoire, exceeding all yield targets.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0 text-sm">2022</div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 flex-1"><strong>Strategic Partnerships</strong> — Partnerships signed with AZUD, Hortalan, World Bank, GIZ and the Ivorian Ministry of Agriculture.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0 text-sm">2023</div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 flex-1"><strong>Pan-African Expansion</strong> — 500+ projects completed across 5 countries including Côte d'Ivoire, Ghana, Burkina Faso, Zimbabwe and Kenya.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0 text-sm">2024</div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 flex-1"><strong>Digital Farming Launch</strong> — IoT-powered smart farming solutions and AI analytics deployed for modern remote farm management.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0 text-sm">2025</div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 flex-1"><strong>Hortalan Joint Venture</strong> — Establishing a landmark JV with Hortalan to open their first branch in Côte d'Ivoire — a milestone for West African agriculture.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Work Together?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Whether you're a farmer, investor, institution or government partner — we want to hear from you.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg hover:bg-primary-600 transition-colors duration-300 inline-block">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
